        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Securing Our Schools Act of &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;b&gt;2024&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill allows states, territories, tribal governments, metropolitan cities, and local governments to use unobligated Coronavirus State and Local Fiscal Recovery Funds to carry out school security measures (e.g., trainings and security assessments).&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
